headline: Keysight Validates First PTCRB New Radio Non-Terrestrial Networks Conformance Test Cases
summary: SANTA ROSA, Calif., November 10, 2025--Keysight Technologies, Inc. (NYSE: KEYS) has validated the first PCS Type Certification Review Board (PTCRB) 5G new radio (NR) non-terrestrial networks (NTN) test cases for 3rd Generation Partnership Project (3GPP) Release 17 (Rel-17) under PTCRB RFT-555. Keysight currently leads in the total number of radio frequency (RF) transmitter and receiver test cases and uniquely holds validated performance test cases. headline: Camtek (CAMT) Surpasses Q3 Earnings and Revenue Estimates
